Source: bosto-tablet
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Jean Parpaillon <jean@parpaillon.info>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), dh-dkms
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: bosto-dkms
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, dkms
Description: BOSTO tablet kernel driver (DKMS)
 HID kernel driver for BOSTO drawing tablets, packaged for
 automatic build via DKMS.

Package: bosto-tools
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: libwacom-common
Description: BOSTO tablet support files
 udev rules and libwacom device definitions for BOSTO drawing
 tablets.

Package: bosto-tablet
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, bosto-dkms (= ${source:Version}), bosto-tools (= ${source:Version})
Description: BOSTO tablet full support (metapackage)
 Metapackage that installs both the DKMS kernel driver and the
 userspace support files for BOSTO drawing tablets.
